data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the coveted Valley View School District! This stunning 3-bedroom, 2 full bath, 2 half bath residence offers an unparalleled living experience, combining modern updates with timeless charm. Step inside and be greeted by a spacious living area featuring a cozy fireplace and built-in shelves, creating the perfect ambiance for relaxing evenings with family and friends. The large kitchen is a chef's delight, boasting ample counter space and top-of-the-line appliances, making meal preparation a breeze. The master suite is a true retreat, with a completely updated master bath that exudes luxury and sophistication. Pamper yourself in the spa-like atmosphere with sleek fixtures and tasteful finishes, providing the ultimate in comfort and relaxation. Enjoy the seamless transition from indoor to outdoor living with a deck that overlooks a sprawling, picturesque backyard. This outdoor oasis is ideal for entertaining guests, hosting barbecues, or simply unwinding after a long day. Convenience is key with a dedicated laundry room, ensuring your household tasks are handled with ease.
